HEADWORD: Sized
<hw>Sized</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Adjusted
according to size.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Having a particular size or magnitude; -- chiefly
used in compounds; <as>as, large-<ex>sized</ex>;
common-<ex>sized</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sizel</ent>⟦br⟧
